{
  "_tutorial_zh": [
    "=== 武器事件脚本配置 ===",
    "此文件定义武器的特殊效果，使用 JavaScript 语法",
    "",
    "事件类型 (event)：",
    "  onHit: 攻击命中时触发",
    "  onKill: 击杀敌人时触发",
    "  onHurt: 自己被攻击时触发",
    "  whenHeld: 主手持有时触发 (每5tick)",
    "",
    "可用变量：",
    "  self: 持有武器的玩家/实体",
    "  victim: 受害者 (onHit/onKill) 或攻击者 (onHurt)",
    "  event: Forge事件对象",
    "",
    "常用API：",
    "  self.heal(2) - 治疗2点血",
    "  victim.setHurtResistantTime(0) - 清空无敌帧",
    "  event.setAmount(event.getAmount() * 1.5) - 伤害倍率",
    "  self.getPotionEffect('poison') - 获取药水效果",
    "  self.addPotionEffect('speed', 200, 1) - 添加药水",
    "",
    "完整API请参考 SCRIPT_API.md"
  ],
  "_tutorial_en": [
    "=== Weapon Event Script Config ===",
    "This file defines special weapon effects using JavaScript syntax",
    "",
    "Event types (event):",
    "  onHit: Triggered when attack hits",
    "  onKill: Triggered when killing an enemy",
    "  onHurt: Triggered when you are attacked",
    "  whenHeld: Triggered while held in main hand (every 5 ticks)",
    "",
    "Available variables:",
    "  self: The player/entity holding the weapon",
    "  victim: The victim (onHit/onKill) or attacker (onHurt)",
    "  event: Forge event object",
    "",
    "Common APIs:",
    "  self.heal(2) - Heal 2 HP",
    "  victim.setHurtResistantTime(0) - Clear invincibility frames",
    "  event.setAmount(event.getAmount() * 1.5) - Damage multiplier",
    "  self.getPotionEffect('poison') - Get potion effect",
    "  self.addPotionEffect('speed', 200, 1) - Add potion effect",
    "",
    "See SCRIPT_API.md for full API reference"
  ],

  "scripts": [
    {
    "_comment": "火焰锭双截棍效果 / Fiery Ingot Nunchaku Effects",
    "id": "fieryingotnunchaku",
      "events": [
        {
        "_comment": "击中时点燃目标3秒 / Set target on fire for 3 seconds on hit",
          "event": "onHit",
        "actions": [
            "victim.setFire(3)"
        ]
        },
        {
        "_comment": "击杀时获得力量效果 / Gain strength on kill",
          "event": "onKill",
        "actions": [
            "self.addPotionEffect('minecraft:strength', 100, 0)"
        ]
        },
        {
        "_comment": "受伤时完全免伤(测试用) / Full damage immunity when hurt (for testing)",
        "event": "onHurt",
        "actions": [
            "event.setAmount(0)"
        ]
        },
        {
            "_comment": "压制所有负面效果到2级 / Suppress all negative effects to level 2",
            "event": "whenHeld",
            "actions": [
                "var negativeEffects = ['minecraft:poison', 'minecraft:wither', 'minecraft:weakness', 'minecraft:slowness', 'minecraft:mining_fatigue', 'minecraft:blindness', 'minecraft:hunger', 'minecraft:nausea'];",
                "for (var i = 0; i < negativeEffects.length; i++) {",
                "  var eff = self.getPotionEffect(negativeEffects[i]);",
                "  if (eff != null && eff.getAmplifier() > 2) {",
                "    self.removePotionEffect(negativeEffects[i]);",
                "    self.addPotionEffect(negativeEffects[i], eff.getDuration(), 2);",
                "  }",
                "}"
            ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
